    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> in 750ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
