      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the onion is softening, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>courgette</strong> and your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 18-20 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 4,
