        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and your <strong>plant based 'Nduja</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>arborio</strong> <strong>rice </strong>and <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the oil</p>",
