    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, stir the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>veg</strong> through the risotto with your <strong>umami</strong> <strong>seasoning</strong>, a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>plant-based 'Nduja & tomato risotto</strong></p>",
